  "title": "A Design and Methods of Analysis to Monitor Crop Growth Conditions Illustrated with Sorghum Screening Trails for Resistance to Striga",
  "abstract": "Checker-board field layouts are used to screen sorghum genotypes for resistance to Striga. A systematic check entry is used to monitor crop growth conditions and methods to analyse the results are assessed.",
